@startuml state_deterministic_fallback_v2
!theme plain
hide empty description

[*] --> Payload_Intercepted : LLD Schema Arrives at Agent 3

state Payload_Intercepted {
  [*] --> Vector_Retrieval
  Vector_Retrieval : Query pgvector for regulatory rules
  Vector_Retrieval --> Model_Inference : Rules Extracted
  
  state Model_Inference {
    [*] --> LLM_Evaluation
    LLM_Evaluation : Evaluate Schema vs Rules via Llama-3-70B
    LLM_Evaluation --> Inference_Success : Valid output parsed
    LLM_Evaluation --> Timeout_Error : TTFT exceeds 10s SLA
    LLM_Evaluation --> Hallucination_Error : Output format invalid
  }
}

Model_Inference --> Deterministic_Fallback : [Timeout OR Hallucination] (Circuit Breaker OPEN)

state Deterministic_Fallback {
  [*] --> Keyword_Matching
  Keyword_Matching : Fallback to strict regex/AST rules
  Keyword_Matching : (No contextual reasoning)
  Keyword_Matching --> Hard_Stop : Violation (e.g., CDE ingress without DPoP)
  Keyword_Matching --> Approved_Fallback : Passed
}

Model_Inference --> Approved_Model : [Inference_Success] (No Violations)
Model_Inference --> Hard_Stop : [Inference_Success] (Violations Found)

Approved_Model --> [*] : Publish Validation OK to Temporal
Approved_Fallback --> [*] : Publish Validation OK (Degraded Mode)
Hard_Stop --> [*] : Publish TRA Alert & Halt Pipeline

note right of Deterministic_Fallback
  <b>Graceful Cognitive Degradation</b>
  If the LLM fails, we bypass the AI
  and rely on deterministic thresholds
  to guarantee system stability.
end note

@enduml
